                "- Physical-form of target is solid.",
                "- Target-thickness: 2 micro-meter for titanium hydride",
                "  and deuteride and 7.5 micro-meter for Kapton"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDEG"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Degraded by titanium foils. Energy losses were",
                "       derived from the stopping power formulated by",
                "       Ziegler [Helium Stopping Powers and Ranges in",
                "       All Elemental Matter, Pergamon Press, NY, 66",
                "       (1977)]."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
